          p Before you can raise your send limit, federal regulations require Remitly to prove your identity.

          p We'll walk you through this process, which typically takes about 10 minutes. If everything looks good, approval is instant and automatic.

          .btn.btn--success.btn--block(id="btn-start")
            | Get Started
        .page.pad-md(id="doc-select")
          .h3
            strong Documents

          p Choose one of these documents to submit

          .radio-card
            .radio-card__radio
              .radio-card__radio-dot
            .radio-card__content
              h4 Driver's License
              p &#9733; Fastest verification
          .radio-card
            .radio-card__radio
              .radio-card__radio-dot
            .radio-card__content
              h4 Passport
          .radio-card
            .radio-card__radio
              .radio-card__radio-dot
            .radio-card__content
              h4 Military I.D.
          .radio-card
            .radio-card__radio
              .radio-card__radio-dot
            .radio-card__content
              h4 Matricular Consular

          .hidden(id="more-docs")
            .radio-card
              .radio-card__radio
                .radio-card__radio-dot
              .radio-card__content
                h4 Even
            .radio-card
              .radio-card__radio
                .radio-card__radio-dot
              .radio-card__content
                h4 More
            .radio-card
              .radio-card__radio
                .radio-card__radio-dot
              .radio-card__content
                h4 Documents

          .btn.btn--blank.btn--subdued.btn--block(id="show-docs")
            | Use something else

          br
          br

          .btn.btn--success.btn--block.is-disabled(id="docs-continue")
            | Continue
        .page.pad-md.bg-color-brand-gray-15(id="capture")
